      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIT THE BUTTON (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 17.16 beating Berringa Black. Well placed and will be tough to beat. MAISEY MARY (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Bendigo over 425m behind Caved In (25.17) in a T3 RSTW. Key player if finds best. BE COURAGEOUS (6) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 17.17 beating Fading Flame. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. JUMBUK FUNI (8) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
